sequenceDiagram
    participant Person as "Admin"
    participant Front as "Browser"
    participant Back as "PHP Backend"
    participant DB as "MySQL"

    Person->>Front: Select project & assign teacher
    Front->>Back: POST /index.php?route=assign
    Back->>DB: UPDATE projects SET teacher_id=?
    DB->>Back: success
    Back->>Back: trigger Notifier (n8n webhook)
    Back->>Front: redirect to dashboard
    Front->>Person: Assignment confirmed